  "text": "Alkaptonuria is an autosomal recessive disorder. The gene for homogentisate oxidase has been mapped to chromosome 3q2, and over 40 mutations have been identified [CITATION_1] . The estimated incidence is between 1:250 000 and 1:1 000 000 live births.",
